## Diferencias con producción (DOKS)

| Aspecto | Staging (RPi) | Producción (DOKS) |
|---|---|---|
| Control plane | k3s self-hosted en RPi 3 | Gestionado por DigitalOcean |
| Base de datos | StatefulSet local en SSD | Managed Postgres DO |
| Redis | StatefulSet local | Managed Redis DO |
| Registry | ghcr.io | DO Container Registry |
| Logs | stdout / kubectl logs | Grafana Cloud (Loki) |
| TLS | cert-manager + Let's Encrypt | cert-manager + Let's Encrypt |
| Autoscaling nodos | No (hardware fijo) | DO cluster autoscaler |
| Manifiestos k8s/ | Mismos | Mismos (solo cambian secrets y registry) |
